description: Have you ever wondered about your origin story? Where did you come from, and does it matter anyway? In this video from Frank Hasel, we take a deep dive into our origin story as humankind. Men, women, old, young, no matter what race or languagewe are all human, and we originate together in one place with one Creator. #Devotionalthought #inspirationalthought #Gospel #Biblestudy #Bibletime #AdventistBeliefs
